# pn-sequence

> A Python library for testing pseudo-noise (PN) sequences

## Install

## Developing

```bash
poetry install
eval $(poetry env activate)
python

# Inside REPL
import pn_sequence
pn_sequence.is_first_postulate_true("011001000111101") # etc.
```

## Testing

```bash
poetry run pytest
```

For coverage:

```bash
poetry run pytest --cov=pn_sequence tests/
```

